Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Fighting back again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:43.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Seems to be like it never ends
